    "In our experiments, we systematically evaluate methods for few-shot learning, that is, using minimal training data, in a lower-resource domain and language, in our case German clinical routine (Hahn and Oleynik 2020; Jantscher et al. 2023; Idrissi-Yaghir et al. 2024).",
